message.text:
LF: 2 REPLACEMENT 
Walking distance to NU/FEU/UST/CEU/UE 
📍Location: Grand Residence 1, España, Sampaloc Manila

DETAILS:
— Monthly Rent: Php 6,000.00/pax (not include bills sa water, electricity, assoc, wifi)
— Payment: 1 month advance, 2 months deposit (18,000 Upon Move in) 

INCLUSIONS
✅ Good for 3 pax
✅ Air Conditioner 
✅ Visitors are allowed 
✅ Cooking is allowed
✅ Has Comfort Room with Shower
✅ Washing Machine
✅ Refrigerator 
✅ Stove
✅ Balcony 
✅ 24/7 cctv security 
✅ Close to CHEAP karenderyas/silogans 
✅ 5 to 10 min walk to UST, NU, FEU
✅ Available for viewing by appointment

AMENITIES
✅ Gym
✅ Sauna
✅ Indoor Pool
✅ Rooftop
✅ Study Area 

🚫 NO PETs

Please send a message if interested, thank you!
